title: The Leslie Speaker - Converse Rubber Tracks: Geek Out
description:
In this segment of Geek Out presented by Guitar Center, Converse Rubber Tracks studio manager Brad Worrell sits down with award winning engineer Justin Douglas, owner of Shine Studios in Austin, TX. Together they show viewers how to create a homemade Leslie speaker. Watch and learn about what a Leslie is, what it can do, and how you too can make one at home for $12. 

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks visit:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
